latestPosts.caption:
A quick intro for those of you who are new here & wonder what I do for a living!

As the CBO of @fynd.commerce, I have learnt so much about fashion & AI over the past 8 years that I now feel it’s time to share with you guys!

AI is taking over the world in more ways that you can imagine, there are such cool things happening & I genuinely believe AI and automation is the way forward, even when it comes to the fashion industry 🤩

Honestly, there’s so much happening in this space and I figured it’s about time I started sharing it with you.

So if you’re into fashion, curious about tech or just want a behind-the-scenes look at what I do - stick around. I’ll be posting more about my work-life at Fynd, my podcast @behindcloseddoorswithfynd and of course a little bit of fashion too! 🫶

(Ragini Varma, CBO, Fynd platform, AI, Fashion AI, Technology, AI thought leader, fashion tech, podcast, narrator trend, corporate fashion, corporate life, fashion creator, explore, AI in India)

Have you ever tried to shoot with kids? Then you must already know it’s a full day workout - handling their tantrums, figuring their sleep schedules, getting them to pose on set & not to forget the 100 mood swings 🤯

At @fynd.commerce we have found the perfect solution to this - AI photoshoots 🫶🏻

All you need to do is select the baby model & give us the clothes & we can generate an entire shoot for you in just 3 days! 

Tag a baby brand below & ask them to try this!
